item.title: CVE-2019-1010124|2024-08-05T03:07:18.228Z -- webappick -- woocommerce%20product%20feed
item.description: WebAppick WooCommerce Product Feed 2.2.18 and earlier is affected by: Cross Site Scripting (XSS). The impact is: XSS to RCE via editing theme files in WordPress. The component is: admin/partials/woo-feed-manage-list.php:63. The attack vector is: Administrator must be logged in.
